{"tid":767462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北戴河會議秘密開始   或討論因貿易戰而來的金融風險   淡化習總的個人形象","createTime":"2018-08-04T13:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T01:59:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4037d43a9d5449e244599222f670d10f69be1f1c","tid":767462,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:59:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【中南海權鬥】領導人集體神隱 分析：北戴河會議已經開始</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180804/58524283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58524283&d=RZ8hy5wQ06NL2BZ5%2FpVUWTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=0342ded4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F58524283&h=d5c1dbbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180804/58524283</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180804/large/1533381722_f5bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180804%2Flarge%2F1533381722_f5bf.jpg&h=7b5884b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那官媒近兩日的報道，均不見中共政治局七常委的蹤影。他們集體神隱，有指一年一度的北戴河會議已經開始。除了支美貿易戰，其中一項議題將是調整「領導風格」，淡化習總的個人形象。<br />\n<br />\n支共中央機關報、領導人活動風向標《人民日報》，自踏入8月，除8月1日頭版有習近平主持中央政治局會議、中共政治局第七次集體學習、黨外人士座談會，與及國務院總理李克強與英國外相侯俊偉會面的消息，8月2、3日均沒有七常委的消息，特別是沒有報道七常委出席八一建軍節活動的新聞。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，新華社報道中央組織部長陳希，受總書記習近平委託，今日與副總理胡春華在北戴河看望62位正休假、以中國兩院院士為主的專家。北戴河所在地河北秦皇島早前已經發佈低空飛行器禁飛領，及進行交通管制，種種跡象顯示，中共領導人已經在北戴河，舉行一年一度的北戴河會議。<br />\n<br />\n多維新聞報道指出，今年的北戴河會議最重要的議題，是如何應對支美貿易戰，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">而隨貿易戰而來的金融風險管控亦是重要議題。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 早前外界亦估計，支共領導與元老們將會討論中共黨建、宣傳問題，不排除可能調整「領導風格」，淡化習總的個人形象，突出「🇨🇳🇨🇳集體領導🇨🇳🇨🇳」。"},{"pid":"32185632c5df477adb54ee0e6e37daae91938b44","tid":767462,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"被人噤住打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0366bf58139c13db795a356ef1f2395c2a041158","tid":767462,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32185632c5df477adb54ee0e6e37daae91938b44","tid":767462,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"被人噤住打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"內部批鬥大會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed36fbfd351edf6003cbed32013229e04c505854","tid":767462,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0366bf58139c13db795a356ef1f2395c2a041158","tid":767462,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32185632c5df477adb54ee0e6e37daae91938b44","tid":767462,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"被人噤住打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:10:28.000Z","msg":"內部批鬥大會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:29:25.000Z","msg":"搵人祭旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3bb30868eac2a0ced2e98f82e42852bd55a5519","tid":767462,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"今日cctv完全無刁總出新聞<img src=\"/assets/fac